1
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:32,440
Fortunately, the Kun Whale came to our aid.

2
00:00:32,760 --> 00:00:33,440
Indeed.

3
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:34,200
That was truly dangerous.

4
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:40,840
What is this?

5
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,000
This is a Merfolk.

6
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:45,480
I heard that in ancient times, Merfolk were very powerful.

7
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:47,120
They rode dragons for travel.

8
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,280
And fed on Kun.

9
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,320
I do not know why they declined later.

10
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,440
Becoming subordinates to the Dragon Clan instead.

11
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:57,560
This background music is actually quite nice.

12
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:58,840
Cover your ears, quickly!

13
00:00:58,840 --> 00:00:59,360
Do not listen!

14
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,600
Why?

15
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,480
It is so dark here.

16
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,360
I cannot see anything.

17
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,480
Yin Guniang.

18
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,640
Where are you?

19
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,360
It is an illusion.

20
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,560
Guard your mind.

21
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:35,720
Do not be afraid.

22
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:36,920
The more you fear it, the stronger it becomes.

23
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,480
Li Jing, is that you?

24
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,400
It is I.

25
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,320
You may open your eyes now.

26
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:03,800
Watch out!

27
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,600
Li Jing!

28
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,920
Rat of the Human Race!

29
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,200
Pay with your life for my descendants!

30
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,560
Thunder of Mutual Destruction!

31
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:25,160
Do not hurt Yu Han!

32
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:30,960
Li Jing.

33
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,520
I have exhausted my Vital Force.

34
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,760
My life will end soon.

35
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,440
Li Jing.

36
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,400
It is all my fault.

37
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,600
I am useless.

38
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,000
I have burdened you.

39
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,720
Flower.

40
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,280
Merfolk flower.

41
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,520
What flower?

42
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:50,400
Where is a flower?

43
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,280
When a Merfolk dies,

44
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,480
The Divine Flower appears.

45
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,480
Quickly.

46
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:05,600
I too once had a beautiful home.

47
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:08,840
Until the iron spears of humans fell.

48
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,400
Hunting my children and grandchildren.

49
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,760
If this vengeance is not taken,

50
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:18,000
I will not rest in peace.

51
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,680
You...

52
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,920
Actually...

53
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,040
Healed completely.

54
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,960
You really scared me to death.

55
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,520
Legends say,

56
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,720
Merfolk have three treasures:

57
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,040
Tears Turn into Pearls,

58
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,160
Dragon Gauze Weaving,

59
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,360
And Everlasting Lamp Oil.

60
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,240
But few actually know,

61
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,040
The most precious thing of the Merfolk,

62
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:48,280
Is the Tricolor Divine Flower formed after their death.

63
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,120
This flower has the power to bring the dead back to life.

64
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,000
Truly the world's finest miracle medicine.

65
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,800
Presumably, the old Merfolk's descendants,

66
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,800
Were hunted by humans for this very reason.

67
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,560
I get the feeling that inside,

68
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,760
There is some monster hiding,

69
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,880
Watching me right now.

70
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,040
The bottomless valley of the East Sea,

71
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,720
Where all waters converge,

72
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,240
Is known as Guixu.

73
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,520
Though the path ahead is fraught with peril,

74
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,200
My life is dedicated to the common people.

75
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,440
Let us go.

76
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:27,640
All descendants of my Dragon Clan bloodline,

77
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,720
Without the decree of the Ancestral Scale,

78
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,680
Those who dare to trespass,

79
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:36,840
Their blood shall dry up,

80
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:39,480
Their souls shall fall forever.

81
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,040
The Dragon Clan's supreme treasure.

82
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:47,520
I knew it wouldn't be that simple.

83
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,800
Li Jing.

84
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,240
Palm Thunder.

85
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,920
Sons of my tribe,

86
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,040
the power of this Xirang

87
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,720
can transform heaven and earth

88
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,680
and overturn the Nine Provinces.

89
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,360
It can summon endless oceans.

90
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,120
Use it with caution.

91
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,320
The seal

92
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:38,720
can only be broken by our bloodline.

93
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,120
This object is too dangerous.

94
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,560
If the Sea Clan obtains it,

95
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,880
the consequences would be unthinkable.

96
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:44,800
Indeed.

97
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,520
But it is strange.

98
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,960
How did Xu Zhong have the map?

99
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,480
Regardless of the reason,

100
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,280
we cannot let the Dragon Clan get it.

101
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,440
This is the Mystic Origin Gourd.

102
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,960
A magical artifact my Master gave me.

103
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,440
It's so tiny.

104
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,280
What is it used for?

105
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,960
Do not underestimate it.

106
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,520
Wind and thunder, make way;

107
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,600
Heaven and earth, enter my belly.

108
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,600
Collect!

109
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,200
It really is a treasure!

110
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:20,160
Oh no!

111
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,400
This place is about to collapse!
